      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### Phase 1: Ad Mediation Telemetry & Infrastructure Chaos Simulation\n",
        "Diagnosing revenue bleed in mobile ad mediation requires analyzing high-volume, unstructured infrastructure logs. I engineered a dataset simulating 1M+ ad requests across diverse hardware profiles, OS versions, and SDK combinations.\n",
        "\n",
        "To rigorously evaluate unsupervised anomaly detection and association rule mining algorithms later in the pipeline, I mathematically injected specific hardware-SDK friction points:\n",
        "* **Silent Fails:** Zero-fill-rate timeouts without fatal exception flags (invisible revenue bleed).\n",
        "* **OOM (Out of Memory) Leaks:** Toxic combinations of low-RAM hardware and specific Rewarded Video SDKs.\n",
        "* **ANR (Application Not Responding):** Thread-blocking latency spikes tied to deprecated OS/SDK interactions."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Cvv6yvwMkoK-"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 1,
